to make dipping consistency , stir remaining ingredients into mixture
form into balls
press and freeze for 1 to 2 months
to serve , remove from freezer and place on serving tray to defrost
cut into 1 / 2 inch squares and place on cooling rack
serve with a scoop of whipped cream
sprinkle with icing sugar before serving
to make a frosting that is of a chewy consistency , place 1 / 2 teaspoon of cream cheese , 1-2 cup of powdered sugar and cinnamon and water in top of an instant-food bag
